    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '1. Levantar una interfaz (router Cisco)

    interface gigabitEthernet
    0/0

    ip address 192.168.1.1 255.255.255.0

    no shutdown

    2. Configurar
    un servidor DHCP en el router

    ip dhcp pool RED1

    network 192.168.1.0
    255.255.255.0

    default-router 192.168.1.1

    exit

    ip dhcp excluded-address
    192.168.1.1 192.168.1.10

    3. Obtener IP por DHCP en VPCS: ip dhcp

    4.
    Asignar IP en VPCS: ip address mask gateway'
